message: Rule applicable: mod_to_bubble ([("Bubble", 6000)]), to expression: y % z, resulting in: {SafeMod(y,z) @ (z != 0)}
Rule applicable: bubble_up ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: x % {SafeMod(y,z) @ (z != 0)}, resulting in: {x % SafeMod(y,z) @ And([(z != 0)])}
Rule applicable: bubble_up ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: ({x % SafeMod(y,z) @ And([(z != 0)])} = 3), resulting in: {(x % SafeMod(y,z) = 3) @ And([And([(z != 0)])])}
Rule applicable: expand_bubble ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: {(x % SafeMod(y,z) = 3) @ And([And([(z != 0)])])}, resulting in: And([(x % SafeMod(y,z) = 3), And([And([(z != 0)])])])
Rule applicable: mod_to_bubble ([("Bubble", 6000)]), to expression: x % SafeMod(y,z), resulting in: {SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) @ (SafeMod(y,z) != 0)}
Rule applicable: bubble_up ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: ({SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) @ (SafeMod(y,z) != 0)} = 3), resulting in: {(SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) = 3) @ And([(SafeMod(y,z) != 0)])}

Rule applicable: expand_bubble ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: {(SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) = 3) @ And([(SafeMod(y,z) != 0)])}, resulting in: And([(SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) = 3), And([(SafeMod(y,z) != 0)])])

Rule applicable: normalise_associative_commutative ([("Base", 8400)]), to expression: And([And([(SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) = 3), And([(SafeMod(y,z) != 0)])]), And([And([(z != 0)])])]), resulting in: And([(SafeMod(x,SafeMod(y,z)) = 3), (SafeMod(y,z) != 0), (z != 0)])

Rule applicable: flatten_binop ([("Minion", 4400)]), to expression: (SafeMod(y,z) != 0), resulting in: (__1 != 0)
